 Manny Pacquiao boxing gear and effects have soared as much as 10 times ahead of his May 2 megafight with Floyd Mayweather .
Online and front-end retailers are seeing record sales of T-shirts , boxing gloves , figurines , with buyers stocking up on items they believe could double in value if he wins .
Prices of Pacquay-autographed boxing gloves have jumped 10 times since February .